  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a challenging journey as you take on the role of a golden bouncy artifact with a singular goal: reach the top of an ancient, enigmatic tower. But beware, for this tower has a will of its own and will stop at nothing to manipulate you to abandon your quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1000 meters of challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scale a kilometer-high tower filled with treacherous obstacles, each more deadly than the next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to learn, hard to master</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and intuitive physics-based controls, brace yourself for a true test of skill and precision as you navigate increasingly demanding challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sentient system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an unexpected journey with a living tower, as she communicates through a vast array of sentences displayed on her walls. Featuring over 1000 unique sentences reflecting moods such as irony, despair, anger, boredom, and much more, you will be drawn into a battle of wits and willpower as you strive to conquer the tower's formidable challenges, all while enduring her relentless provocations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those that decide to buy the game, thank you so so much, it means the world to me!!!  And remember:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >May your climb be swift and your determination unbreakable!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a challenging journey as you take on the role of a golden bouncy artifact with a singular goal: reach the top of an ancient, enigmatic tower. But beware, for this tower has a will of its own and will stop at nothing to manipulate you to abandon your quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1000 meters of challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scale a kilometer-high tower filled with treacherous obstacles, each more deadly than the next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to learn, hard to master</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and intuitive physics-based controls, brace yourself for a true test of skill and precision as you navigate increasingly demanding challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sentient system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an unexpected journey with a living tower, as she communicates through a vast array of sentences displayed on her walls. Featuring over 1000 unique sentences reflecting moods such as irony, despair, anger, boredom, and much more, you will be drawn into a battle of wits and willpower as you strive to conquer the tower's formidable challenges, all while enduring her relentless provocations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For those that decide to buy the game, thank you so so much, it means the world to me!!!  And remember:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >May your climb be swift and your determination unbreakable!</p>",
